<li><em> Engineering Safety Aspects of the Protection of Nuclear Power Plants Against Sabotage</em>. Agence internationale de l&#8217;&eacute;nergie atomique, Collection S&eacute;curit&eacute; nucl&eacute;aire n<sup>o</sup> 4, 2007.</li>
